snippet.title: Lemuria: Lost in Space - official launch trailer
snippet.description:
Lemuria: Lost in space is a unique adventure, full of mysteries, puzzles and shocking discoveries.
Explore the long-lost Lemuria 7 spaceship and find out what happened to the crew.

Play now: http://store.steampowered.com//app/563250

Lemuria: Lost in space will be available on Steam from 17th March.
